Team
LBC Credit Partners is a team of leading industry veterans who possess an average of 20 years experience in principal investing, corporate restructuring, corporate finance and business operations. Due to our diverse backgrounds and substantial expertise, our team is able to quickly evaluate and decisively structure a wide range of transaction types from buyouts to restructurings. LBC team members are commonly referred to as "trusted advisors" by clients and the financial community.

